## Architecture

### Route Groups

```
app/
â”śâ”€â”€ (auth)/sso-login-complete/   # SSO callback â€” runs OUTSIDE providers
â””â”€â”€ (app)/                       # Authenticated routes â€” wrapped by AppShell
    â”śâ”€â”€ layout.tsx               # AppShell + providers
    â””â”€â”€ page.tsx                 # Home page
```

The SSO callback is in `(auth)/` to avoid the auth provider deadlock â€” it must store tokens before `AuthProvider` initializes.

### Providers (`providers/index.tsx`)

```
AuthProvider > TenantProvider > {children}
```

`initializeDataLayer` is called synchronously in a `useState` initializer with **5 arguments** (data-layer v1.2+):

```typescript
initializeDataLayer(dmUrl, lmsUrl, legacyLmsUrl, storageService, httpErrorHandler)
```

This must happen before any child component's RTK Query hooks fire.

### Redux Store (`store/index.ts`)

```typescript
coreApiSlice      // Core IBL API endpoints
mentorReducer     // Mentor/user/tenant API slices
mentorMiddleware  // RTK Query middleware for all slices
```

`@reduxjs/toolkit` is deduplicated via webpack `resolve.alias` in `next.config.ts`. Without deduplication, SDK components use a different `ReactReduxContext` and RTK Query hooks silently return `undefined` with zero HTTP requests.

### Pre-built Components (`components/iblai/`)

| Component | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| `ChatWidget` | `<mentor-ai>` web component wrapper â€” full-screen AI chat |
| `ProfileDropdown` | Avatar dropdown with profile link and logout |
| `IblaiNotificationBell` | Bell icon with unread count badge |

{% if has_mentor_id %}
### `<mentor-ai>` Web Component

Auth tokens are delivered via `redirectToAuthSPA()` which sends `{ ...localStorage }` to the iframe when `authrelyonhost="true"`. The method name is misleading â€” it does NOT redirect when `authRelyOnHost` is true; it posts a message instead.

{% endif %}
## Environment (`.env.local`)

```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.iblai.app        # Consolidated API base
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_URL=https://login.iblai.app            # Auth SPA URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_WS_URL=wss://asgi.data.iblai.app     # WebSocket endpoint
NEXT_PUBLIC_PLATFORM_BASE_DOMAIN=iblai.app             # Fallback domain pattern
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAIN_TENANT_KEY=your-main-platform           # Platform key
{% if has_mentor_id %}
NEXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_AGENT_ID=your-mentor-id            # Mentor/agent ID
{% endif %}
```

Copy `.env.example` to `.env.local` and fill in your values.

